获取当前页面的高度 <strong>document.body.scrollHeight</strong>
<pre>parent.document.getElementById("_work").style.height = (<strong>document.body.scrollHeight</strong>)+px;</pre>
下面这种写法，可能没有效果
<pre>比如有个iframe_content的iframe
通过：<del><span style="color: #ff0000;">parent.iframe_content.style.height</span></del> = “800px”; 会无效。
要写成：<span style="color: #99cc00;">parent.document.getElementById("iframe_contentlistshow").style.height = “800px”; </span></pre>
iframe onload事件修改高度 ，兼容写法
<pre>&lt;iframe scrolling="no" frameborder="no" border="0" id="show_content" src="..." onload="dyniframesize('show_content');" style="width:100%;height:480px;"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;

function dyniframesize(obj) {
var pTar = null;
pTar = document.getElementById(obj);

if (pTar.Document.body.scrollHeight &lt; 480) {
pTar.style.height = 480 + "px";
parent.document.getElementById("divContent").style.height = 480 + "px";
parent.parent.document.getElementById("_work").style.height = 482 + "px";
parent.parent.document.getElementById("main").style.height = 482 + "px";
} else {
pTar.style.height = pTar.Document.body.scrollHeight + "px";
parent.document.getElementById("divContent").style.height = pTar.Document.body.scrollHeight + "px";
parent.parent.document.getElementById("_work").style.height = (pTar.Document.body.scrollHeight + 2) + "px";
parent.parent.document.getElementById("main").style.height = (pTar.Document.body.scrollHeight + 2) + "px";
}
}</pre>

